author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Flore Laurentienne performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded September 20, 2024.

Songs:
Fugue 00:50
Navigation IV 07:11
Canon 11:18
Fleuve V (l​é​ger retour) 15:26
Soir 19:21

Mathieu David Gagnon - Composer & Synthesizer
Jean-Christophe Lizotte - Cello
Mélanie Bélair - Violin I
